  "name": "RPlog_HIMS_Predator_Day_1",
  "title": "Aboard the Predator, Day One",
  "summary": "On the observation deck of the Sith Star Destroyer Predator, hidden in the Bothan system near the bombarded world of Cochran, Captain Antoine Dareus reunites with Dr. Lynae Cassius, who is weighing his and Darth Malign's offer of command aboard the modified Interdictor Noquella's Embrace. Over caf and water, the two reflect on Dareus's redemption, his terminal condition, and Lynae's homesickness and unspoken love of the Empire, before the Sith lord Malign joins them and draws Lynae into a sweeping philosophical exchange about death, the Force, war as a wound to be healed, and the nature of order. Malign demonstrates a lightsaber-resistant prototype combat droid born of 'Sith alchemy' and rouses the room with an impassioned vision of resurrecting lost Sith knowledge from dead worlds. The smuggler Axel Vichten arrives to receive his charge from Malign, to cause disruption and draw the galaxy's attention, before he and Lynae linger over drinks discussing Caspian politics, his vow to the Sarian Shadow Brotherhood, and a chilling proposal to engineer a planet-scale biological weapon to destroy crops, which Lynae coolly assesses as feasible.",
